msgid ""
"If you are still experiencing audio related issues, and the above real-time "
"playback factors did not resolve your issue, here are some additional "
"troubleshooting steps you can take."
msgstr ""
"Ako i dalje imate problema sa zvukom, a gore navedeni faktori reprodukcije u "
"stvarnom vremenu nisu riješili vaš problem, evo nekoliko dodatnih koraka za "
"rješavanje problema koje možete poduzeti."

