# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../playback.rst:101
msgid ""
"Check that the Playback Audio Device is set correctly for your sound output "
"under Preferences in the Preview tab. Restart OpenShot after changing the "
"settings. You can also try a different audio device (USB, audio over HDMI "
"from the video card, headphones, etc.) to rule out other audio issues. "
"Disable `automatic sound suppression` for voice calls during microphone "
"activity, and disable `Audio Enhancements` under the advanced settings tab "
"of your audio device (not all audio devices have these settings). See :ref:"
"`preferences_preview_ref`."
msgstr ""
"Provjerite je li Playback Audio Device ispravno postavljen za vaš zvučni "
"izlaz u Postavkama pod karticom Pregled. Ponovno pokrenite OpenShot nakon "
"promjene postavki. Također možete isprobati drugi audio uređaj (USB, zvuk "
"preko HDMI-a s grafičke kartice, slušalice itd.) kako biste isključili druge "
"audio probleme. Onemogućite `automatic sound suppression` za glasovne pozive "
"tijekom aktivnosti mikrofona i onemogućite `Audio Enhancements` u naprednim "
"postavkama vašeg audio uređaja (nisu svi audio uređaji imaju ove postavke). "
"Pogledajte :ref:`preferences_preview_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../playback.rst:107
msgid "Audio Buffer Size"
msgstr "Veličina audio bafera"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../playback.rst:107
msgid ""
"The audio buffer size is the amount of audio samples which must first be "
"buffered in OpenShot before audio playback can begin. If this value is too "
"low, you might experience audio break-up / crackle / popping. If this value "
"is too high, you might experience delays or lag before audio playback "
"begins. OpenShot defaults this value to 512, which is a reasonable default "
"for most systems, which should provide smooth audio playback with minimal "
"noticeable lag or delay. However, on some systems this value might need to "
"be adjusted up or down, for in-sync and lag-free audio playback. The range "
"is 128 to 4096."
msgstr ""
"Veličina audio bafera je količina audio uzoraka koja se mora prvo pohraniti "
"u OpenShot prije nego što reprodukcija zvuka može započeti. Ako je ova "
"vrijednost preniska, možete iskusiti prekide, šumove ili pucanje zvuka. Ako "
"je vrijednost previsoka, možete iskusiti kašnjenja ili zastajkivanja prije "
"početka reprodukcije zvuka. OpenShot zadano postavlja ovu vrijednost na 512, "
"što je razumna zadana vrijednost za većinu sustava i treba omogućiti glatku "
"reprodukciju zvuka s minimalnim primjetnim kašnjenjem. Međutim, na nekim "
"sustavima ovu vrijednost treba prilagoditi gore ili dolje za sinkroniziranu "
"i bezkašnjenja reprodukciju zvuka. Raspon je od 128 do 4096."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../playback.rst:113
msgid "Sample Rate"
msgstr "Frekvencija uzorkovanja"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../playback.rst:113
msgid ""
"Ensure that the `Default Audio Sample Rate` and `Default Audio Channels` on "
"the Preview tab of the Preferences window match your hardware. You can also "
"check these settings in the operating system control panel (i.e. Windows "
"Sound Control Panel). See :ref:`preferences_preview_ref`."
msgstr ""
"Provjerite da `Default Audio Sample Rate` i `Default Audio Channels` na "
"kartici Pregled u prozoru Postavki odgovaraju vašem hardveru. Također možete "
"provjeriti ove postavke u upravljačkoj ploči operativnog sustava (npr. "
"Windows Sound Control Panel). Pogledajte :ref:`preferences_preview_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../playback.rst:116
msgid "Volume"
msgstr "Glasnoća"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../playback.rst:116
msgid ""
"Ensure that the volume does not exceed 100% on overlapping clips (such as an "
"audio track combined with a video track). Lower the volume on individual "
"clips if needed. See :ref:`clip_volume_mixing_ref`."
msgstr ""
"Provjerite da glasnoća ne prelazi 100% na preklapajućim isječcima (kao što "
"je audio zapis kombiniran s video zapisom). Po potrebi smanjite glasnoću "
"pojedinačnih isječaka. Pogledajte :ref:`clip_volume_mixing_ref`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../playback.rst:118
msgid "Headphones"
msgstr "Slušalice"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../playback.rst:118
msgid ""
"If you're using headphones, plug them in before starting OpenShot. Launching "
"OpenShot with no speakers, headphones, or valid audio playback device can "
"cause OpenShot to freeze during playback."
msgstr ""
"Ako koristite slušalice, priključite ih prije pokretanja OpenShota. "
"Pokretanje OpenShota bez zvučnika, slušalica ili valjanog audio uređaja za "
"reprodukciju može uzrokovati da se OpenShot zamrzne tijekom reprodukcije."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../playback.rst:120
msgid "OS Updates"
msgstr "Ažuriranja operativnog sustava"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../playback.rst:120
msgid ""
"Update your operating system and any pending security updates. Some audio "
"issues, especially audio device specific issues, can be resolved with an "
"operating system update."
msgstr ""
"Ažurirajte svoj operativni sustav i sva čekajuća sigurnosna ažuriranja. Neki "
"problemi sa zvukom, posebno oni specifični za audio uređaje, mogu se "
"riješiti ažuriranjem operativnog sustava."
